<div id="about" class="row">

  <div id="map_options" class="col-xs-12 col-md-7 col-lg-6">
    <form>
      <p>Start: <input type="text" name="start" id="start" autocomplete="on" value="Pittsburgh, PA"/>
      End: <input type="text" name="end" id="end" autocomplete="on" value="New York, NY"/></p>
      <p>How many
        <select id="method" class="input-lg" style="color:black" >
          <p><option value="hours">hours</option>
          <option value="miles">miles</option></p>
        </select>
        in would you like to stop?
        <input style="color:black" type="number" max="40" min="0.5" step="0.5" name="hours" id="stop_point_hours" value="3.5"/>
        <input style="color:black" type="number" max="3000" min="0" step="25" name="miles" id="stop_point_miles" value="100"/>
      <p>How far away from your route would you like to deviate?
      <select id="mtd" class="input-lg" >
        <p><option value="1609">1</option>
        <option selected="selected" value="8046">5</option>
        <option value="16093">10</option></p>
      </select> miles</p>
      <p>What's important to you?
      <input type="radio" id="sort" name="sort" value="1" class=".radio-inline">  Closest     
      <input type="radio" id="sort" name="sort" value="2" class=".radio-inline">  Highest rated</p>
      <input class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" type="submit" id="map_options_submit">
    </form>
  </div>

  <div id="blurb" class="col-xs-12 col-md-5 col-lg-6">
    <p>Go on a lot of road trips?</p>
    <p>Ever get sick of horrible rest stop food?</p>
    <p>Check to see if there's something nicer on your way!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" id="search_again_button">
    Search Again
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-8">
      <div id="map" style='height: 400px;'></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
      <div id="directions-panel" style='height: 400px; overflow: scroll; background: white'></div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>



